To run these test in eclipse,
Click on Run from eclipse menu bar 
Click on Run Configurations
Click on Junit Option Right Click and Create a new Run Configuration
This will bring a window with options to Add a name to configuration
Pick the Project in this case "evalSelenium"
and Click on the radio button to Run All Test...
Click on the Arguments tabs and add the following to the VM Arguments sections.

-Dselenium.server.host=localhost
-Dselenium.server.port=4444
-Dselenium.browser.startCommand=*firefox
-Dselenium.browser.url="Replace this with url of the server that you are writing tests"